{"tid":1573493,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我宣布由今日起，所有藍屍組織既活動必須要預先通報","createTime":"2019-09-16T04:18:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-16T04:49:19.000Z","uid":125079,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"87cb360bf2d37e26e05d465b65770c97ee825dae","tid":1573493,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:18:48.000Z","msg":"係所有，包括拆僆儂牆，唱國歌，遊行示威打人等等，卧底一收到消息必須要盡快宣傳<br />\n<br />\n早幾日淘大，炮台山，將軍澳事件，就係好多手足唔知，然後係街上比人打，然後再激起其他手足引唔住去，最後比狗拉比狗打<br />\n<br />\n要知道依加班狗一定死保佢地，而班垃圾藍屍廢老既片段係比中共黨媒睇，我地要做好準備<br />\n<br />\n1. 可以冷處理，所有手足唔理仆街，但後果係可能慢慢令佢地聚集起黎，同埋中央又有好畫面<br />\n<br />\n2. 主動準備，64文宣，新疆事件，中央冇畫面，到時踩場派，但可能比狗捉，就如淘大一樣<br />\n<br />\n3. 卧底入去，影相，私了<br />\n<br />\n但點都好，一定要令全世界知班藍屍會去邊同做咩，因為只要全世界一知，香港人就會唔敢去個度，因為驚衝突驚狗，例如逼商場既要關門<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n同埋最重要係，我地可以做好準備，唔係再等手足比佢地打完先知咩事</span></span><br />\n<br />\n依加已知 918 921有活動 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CHDLw8U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCHDLw8U.jpg&h=fc65221a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QhNo3fD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQhNo3fD.jpg&h=a05e9c12&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ab1be5abe35adbe8cd909a4992d78c0ae2074567","tid":1573493,"uid":308567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:20:48.000Z","msg":"屌你今日都有啦 我開post 冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f1b0996df692cb735abba60004d0eff3ef9dece","tid":1573493,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:21:13.000Z","msg":"918 921 有藍屍活動 各位有咩建議"},{"pid":"4e0d27273941ccf4cd0774e7e827c29a0ca917a8","tid":1573493,"uid":308567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:21:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N32Hzou.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN32Hzou.jpg&h=77b703a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在香港的同胞，9月18日下午1点30分至2点3O分，举目香港万人爱国，爱港人士集合尖沙嘴 ，游行唱国歌，希望各位同胞們勇跃参加活動！手拉手齊唱愛國歌曲，中国加油！中国香港加油！<br />\n<br />\n🇨🇳活動時間: 9.18日1:30pm-2:30pm(請提前15分鐘集合)<br />\n🇨🇳集合地點: 尖沙咀太子酒店<br />\n🇨🇳活動路線: 太子酒店&mdash;天星碼頭<br />\n🇨🇳活動曲目: 中華人民共和國國歌/歌唱祖國<br />\n🇨🇳著裝要求: 請勿著黑色上衣，請勿戴口罩；如有國旗/香港區旗，請攜帶出席<br />\n<br />\n⭐注: 本活動已獲警方批准，請號召親友共同參加<br />\n<br />\n🔵請支持及訂閱🔵<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/wearebluec\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwearebluec&d=qpM4horlrIen4ao1f4l1xZ2AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=eaa7275f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/wearebluec</a>"},{"pid":"6e82937db12ca603f9bcdf00d1e9a3713b511c98","tid":1573493,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab1be5abe35adbe8cd909a4992d78c0ae2074567","tid":1573493,"uid":308567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:20:48.000Z","msg":"屌你今日都有啦 我開post 冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:21:47.000Z","msg":"P牌難推 依加幫你"},{"pid":"9016ea71de2d4eb29c5c6a2cb05937115958a930","tid":1573493,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:21:59.000Z","msg":"全部人入黎呀"},{"pid":"9ecb783b77633063822d1fdbb388ae5155bae13e","tid":1573493,"uid":42942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:22:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"791ada16d22264802ce3a3987e83ce5c6131d0a2","tid":1573493,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:22:28.000Z","msg":"918 藍屍 921 何妖<br />\n<br />\n大家點做 傾好咗先"},{"pid":"1d6bd891ded0014d5327edc892036fe20d3c7079","tid":1573493,"uid":134054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T04:22:56.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PefFk3W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i